0.5	2016-Apr
	change handling of Vienna RNA lib in configure: use pkg-config
	fix distribution to include all necessary files
	add Travis support for CI testing on github
	clean dependencies
0.4	2015-Nov
	add option --noGC to turn off garbage collection
0.3     2015-May
	Bugfixes
	Use gengetopt for command line parsing
	Rename package and program to SparseMFEFold
	Print candidate and trace arrow with option verbose (default off)
	Mark candidates by square brackets with option mark-candidates (default off)
	Produce output identitcal to RNAfold -d0 in default mode

0.2	2015-Feb-24
	RNA folding equivalent to RNAfold -d0; with space efficient
	sparsification and sparse trace-back

0.1	2015-Feb-21
	Avoid trace arrows to candidates to save more space; almost
	Zuker-like RNA folding algorithm (w/o true multi-loops)
	with space efficient sparse trace-back.
